{"arkId":"cl010115646","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010115646","modified ":"2025-09-02","title":"Cylindre : bacchanale avec les M\u00e9nades tentant d\u0027\u00e9veiller Sil\u00e8ne endormi","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cylindre : bacchanale avec les M\u00e9nades tentant d\u0027\u00e9veiller Sil\u00e8ne endormi"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1650 - 1716","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 527 - Adolphe Rothschild, Vitrine 5","room":"Salle 527, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1650,"endYear":1716,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe-XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Hurdter, Johann Ulrich","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1716 ?","place":"","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1631","place":"","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"bibliographie\/travail de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 359","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"chope","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Sil\u00e8ne, ivre, est vautr\u00e9 sur un lion, soutenu avec peine par un bacchant et une bacchante. Autour de lui se d\u00e9cha\u00eenent ses compagnons, qui versent \u00e0 boire, jouent des cymbales ou lui truissent des couronnes de pampres, sans le ramener \u00e0 la conscience. Ni le vacarme des m\u00e9nades ni le jus de sriasins ne r\u00e9veillent le bacchant \u00e0 sa droite, qui \u00e9treint encore un pichet dans son sommeil. A gauche, devant un herm\u00e8s de Priape (?), un satyre est en train de ferrer un \u00e2ne, la monture de Sil\u00e8ne. L\u0027incident est s\u00fbrement la cause de cette halte bruyante du cort\u00e8ge.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; Nro. 102 (manuscrite, \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1,2","displayDimension":"1,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"0,15","displayDimension":"0,15 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"13","displayDimension":"13 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"13,5","displayDimension":"13,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant","placeOfCreation":"Allemagne (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Brunswick, collection ducales, n\u00b0 102 ; saisie en butin lors de la campagne d\u0027Allemagne en 1806","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"saisie napol\u00e9onienne","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1806","startYear":1806,"endYear":1806}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"saisie napol\u00e9onienne"}],"period":[{"value":"\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime"}],"place":[{"value":"Allemagne"}],"objectType":[{"value":"chope"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Malgouyres, Philippe ; Martinez, Jean-Luc (dir.), Venus d\u0027ailleurs. Mat\u00e9riaux et objets voyageurs, cat. exp. (Paris